if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('PackageList')
and type = 'U')
drop table PackageList
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: PackageList */
/*==============================================================*/
create table PackageList (
ID integer not null,
CompanyName varchar(200) not null,
PN varchar(50) null,
ProdNO varchar(50) not null,
ProdName varchar(200) not null,
NumOfBox int null,
FileNO varchar(50) null,
PackageNO varchar(50) null,
PackageModel varchar(50) null,
GlueBoxNO varchar(50) null,
GlueBoxModel varchar(50) null,
GluePackageModel varchar(50) null,
GluePackageNum int null,
LongKnifeModel varchar(50) null,
LongKnifeNum int null,
ShortKnifeModel varchar(50) null,
ShortKnifeNum int null,
BlockOffCardModel varchar(50) null,
BlockOffCardNum int null,
FlatCardModel varchar(50) null,
FlatCardNum int null,
AbsorbPlasticModel varchar(50) null,
AbsorbPlasticNum int null,
Notice varchar(200) null,
PagkagePhoto image null,
PagkagePhotoType varchar(50) null,
PackageType varchar(50) null,
CellLineNum int null,
LineNum int null,
CellPCS int null,
BoxNum int null,
TotalPCS int null,
CellBlockOff int null,
FlatCard int null,
NewVer int null,
ChangedVer int null,
EffectDate datetime null,
NewOldChangedFlag int null,
NewOldVer int null,
OldType varchar(50) null,
OldType_BoxNum int null,
OldType_Num int null,
OldType_CellNum int null,
OldType_BoxPCS int null,
OldType_GlueModel varchar(50) null,
OldType_Other varchar(50) null,
TableMaker varchar(50) null,
Checker varchar(50) null,
EffectedDate datetime null,
QCChecker varchar(50) null,
VerNO varchar(50) not null,
TableNO varchar(50) not null,
constraint PK_PACKAGELIST primary key ()
WITH (IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF) ON [PRIMARY]
)
ON [PRIMARY] TEXTIMAGE_ON [PRIMARY]
go
